import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Switch } from 'react-router-dom'
import { Navbar, Sidebar, Footer } from './components'
import { Home, About, Team, Error } from './pages'

function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
      <Switch>
        <Route exact path='/'>
          <Home />
        </Route>
        <Route exact path='/*'>
          <Error />
        </Route>
      </Switch>
      <Footer />
    </Router>
  )
}

export default App
